configparam.description: tableSchemaName - name of schema in DC tableDiskName - name of table on disk/process region - daas region source - daas source dataClass - daas dataClass subClass - daas subClass dataType - daas dataType symCol - col with attr, to be used to filter with symList in API symColType - type of the sym col (-11) alternateSymCol - can ignore - list of alternate columns that can be used with idType - TBD if needed timeCol - default time column to be filtered by start/end date/time ( should always be timestamp alternateTimeCol - can be used with the `time param to filter on difffernt time col dateCol - date type or timestamp type column which can be used to determine max/min dates for data present keyColumns - columns keyed on when upserting new data diskLayout - how data is written to disk - if partitioned then date,month or year. Otherwise, flat or splayed
